original: Lundin, Bengt, tandläkare, Nybro, f. 22/3/17 i Emmaboda, Kalmar 1., av skohandl. Ernst L. o. Elsa Jonsson. G. 43 m. Dagmar Friberg. Barn: Christer f. 44. — Stud:ex. i Kalmar 37,^ tandhkand. 39, tandl:ex. 42. Vik. i Äseda o. Nybro 43, praktik i Nybro sed. 43.
translated: Lundin, Bengt, dentist, Nybro, b. 22/3/1917 in Emmaboda, Kalmar 1., son of shoe trader Ernst L. and Elsa Jonsson. Married in 1943 to Dagmar Friberg. Children: Christer b. 1944. Education: passed final exams in Kalmar in 1937, dental student in 1939, dental degree in 1942. Worked temporarily in Äseda and Nybro in 1943, established practice in Nybro since 1943.
